78
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,280
Good morning.

79
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,320
Morning...

80
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,920
Good morning, Ms. Rose.

81
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,760
Who would wake up sleeping next to her?

82
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:03,280
Well,

83
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:03,920
Yao,

84
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,640
have a seat here.

85
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,920
Go back inside and put on some clothes.

86
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,160
Yao.

87
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,480
Why are you here this early morning?

88
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,680
Yamamoto will be holding a banquet.

89
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,960
Boss wants you to join it.

90
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,480
(Yamamoto...)

91
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,040
(That's a Japanese.)

92
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:36,640
Today?

93
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:38,800
Now.

94
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,600
Oh?

95
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,760
If so, I'll go get ready now.

96
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:46,640
Go ahead.

97
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,400
Get yourself ready.

98
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:48,880
I'll wait for you here.

99
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,560
You should wait outside.

100
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:54,660
Wait for me out there.

101
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,200
I was standing there for so long.

102
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,200
Wait...

103
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,620
It's all right to wait for you in there.

104
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:00,720
Wait...

105
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:01,480
Hey.

106
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,200
Hurry up.

107
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:10,840
What's the matter?

108
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:12,000
You seem distracted.

109
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,640
Yamamoto

110
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:14,600
is a Japanese?

111
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,520
Zhou Musheng.

112
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,640
Quick.

113
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,480
Coming.

114
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,040
I'm off.

115
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,040
Mm.

116
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,080
Xu.

117
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,840
Head to the tailor's.

118
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,840
Your outfits are ready.

119
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,440
That was fast.

120
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,600
Didn't you say it'd take several days?

121
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,200
Those outfits are for you.

122
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:43,240
