of North City Chamber of Commerce,

146
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:38,080
I will take our chamber of commerce

147
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,240
to new heights.

148
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:44,360
It belongs to me

149
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,640
